  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="KT46-kilavi">piriviṭai āṟṟāḷ eṉak kavaṉṟa tōḻikkuk kiḻatti “āṟṟuval” eṉpatupaṭac colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">She speaking in order to express “I have the strength”, to the confidante who was anxious she might not have the strength in the time of separation.</p>
          </div>



        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="KT46">
<l>                āmpaṟ pūviṉ cāmpa laṉṉa</l>
<l>                kūmpiya ciṟakar maṉaiyuṟai kurīi</l>
<l>                muṉṟi luṇaṅkaṉ mānti maṉṟat</l>
<l>                teruvi ṉuṇṭātu kuṭaivaṉa vāṭi</l>
<l>                yilliṟaip paḷḷittam piḷḷaiyoṭu vatiyum</l>
<l>                puṉkaṇ mālaiyum pulampu</l>
<l>                miṉṟuko ṟōḻiyavar ceṉṟa nāṭṭē.</l>

             </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
             <l rend="indent">In the country where he has gone,</l>
             <l>aren't there, friend, sorrowful evenings and loneliness</l>
             <l rend="indent">when the birds that stay in the house, wings folded</l>
             <l rend="indent">like the withered flowers of the waterlily,</l>
             <l rend="indent">after picking corn in the front-yard [and] playing while</l>
             <l rend="indent">working through the particles of dung in the village common</l>
             <l rend="indent">roost with their children in a nest beneath the eaves of the roof?</l>
                
                </lg>
        </div>
